---- MODULE RoomLifecycle ----
\* Room process lifecycle. Rooms are created on first join and terminate after idle timeout with no participants.
\* Generated by tlaiser — https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

\* State constants — each represents a distinct state
CONSTANTS Empty, Active, IdleTimeout

\* Variables tracked by this specification
VARIABLES state, participant_count, max_participants

\* Type invariant: state is always one of the declared states
TypeInvariant == state \in {Empty, Active, IdleTimeout}

\* Initial state predicate
Init ==
    /\ state = Empty
    /\ participant_count = 0
    /\ max_participants = 50

\* Transition actions
\* Transition: Empty -> Active (participant_joins)
participant_joins ==
    /\ state = Empty
    /\ participant_count < max_participants
    /\ state' = Active
    /\ participant_count := participant_count + 1
    /\ UNCHANGED <<participant_count, max_participants>>

\* Transition: Active -> Active (participant_joins)
participant_joins ==
    /\ state = Active
    /\ participant_count < max_participants
    /\ state' = Active
    /\ participant_count := participant_count + 1
    /\ UNCHANGED <<participant_count, max_participants>>

\* Transition: Active -> Active (participant_leaves)
participant_leaves ==
    /\ state = Active
    /\ participant_count > 1
    /\ state' = Active
    /\ participant_count := participant_count - 1
    /\ UNCHANGED <<participant_count, max_participants>>

\* Transition: Active -> Empty (last_participant_leaves)
last_participant_leaves ==
    /\ state = Active
    /\ participant_count = 1
    /\ state' = Empty
    /\ participant_count := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED <<participant_count, max_participants>>

\* Transition: Empty -> IdleTimeout (idle_timeout_fires)
idle_timeout_fires ==
    /\ state = Empty
    /\ state' = IdleTimeout
    /\ UNCHANGED <<participant_count, max_participants>>

\* Transition: IdleTimeout -> Empty (terminate)
terminate ==
    /\ state = IdleTimeout
    /\ state' = Empty
    /\ UNCHANGED <<participant_count, max_participants>>

\* Next-state relation: disjunction of all transitions
Next ==
    \/ participant_joins
    \/ participant_joins
    \/ participant_leaves
    \/ last_participant_leaves
    \/ idle_timeout_fires
    \/ terminate

\* All variables tuple (for stuttering)
vars == <<state, participant_count, max_participants>>

\* Complete specification
Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_vars

\* Fair specification (with weak fairness on Next)
FairSpec == Spec /\ WF_vars(Next)

\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: MutedParticipantNeverSpeaking (safety)
MutedParticipantNeverSpeaking == []([][ParticipantVoiceState = Muted => ~is_speaking]_ParticipantVoiceState)

\* Property: RoomNeverExceedsMaxParticipants (safety)
RoomNeverExceedsMaxParticipants == []([][participant_count <= max_participants]_participant_count)

\* Property: NegotiationEventuallyCompletes (liveness)
NegotiationEventuallyCompletes == <>(<>(PeerNegotiation = Connected))


====
